        p
          | We now provide 1 night of hotel stay at the local Fairfield Inn, Marriott for each traveling team traveling from outside a 300 mile radius from the school(3 rooms per team). We can also contact Flightline, an airport shuttle service to and from Boston and Manchester, if you would like; however, you will have to cover the expense of the shuttle yourself.
          | If you are interested, please email us at 
